{"tid":782108,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高中老師猥褻25男童、拍性侵影片　重判28年","createTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T06:48:06.000Z","uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbef2c556a7c80f26513a99119d982e41827f7d5","tid":782108,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"一名私立高中男老師，涉嫌誘騙國小、國中男童，到家中猥褻甚至性侵，還拍影片紀錄！案件去年曝光，警方到楠梓家搜索，發現了大批男童裸照和性侵、猥褻影片，被害人多達25名男童。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/07/18/20180718120044-2b462206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F20180718120044-2b462206.jpg&h=1d478ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／TVBS<br />\n<br />\n林姓男老師對25名男童伸出狼爪，台北地院是依加重強制性交，和加重強制猥褻，判他28年徒刑，民事部分則必須賠償，12名男童和家屬710萬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/07/18/20180718120059-d88bd1e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F20180718120059-d88bd1e2.jpg&h=db80c4ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／TVBS<br />\n<br />\n事件會曝光，因為其中一名男童母親，發現兒子臉書跟陌生男子有親密對話。一問之下才知道，男子把男童帶回家，不只播色情片給他看，還摸男童下體猥褻，甚至，同班還有2名男同學受害，男童母親才通知學校老師了解。而警方搜索林姓男子住家，查扣隨身碟、手機、平板、筆電和電腦跟硬碟，發現有各式各樣男童裸照，和他性侵男童、猥褻男童的影片，時間從2009到2017年，25名受害者，大多都未滿14歲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/07/18/20180718120052-d4bc0110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F20180718120052-d4bc0110.jpg&h=4973e540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／TVBS<br />\n<br />\n而這名男子其實是名資訊老師，在北市私立高中任教，他被收押後，校方立刻將他解職，並調查校內同學，沒有發現有人受害。<br />\n<br />\n法官認為，林姓男子為人師表，卻誘騙邁入青春期的國小、國中男童，性交、猥褻過程還拍片紀錄珍藏，開庭時毫無賠償誠意，因此重判28年。"},{"pid":"60d7fc3bccb8174034deae9a36d484298dff389f","tid":782108,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jhUahBc_iyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjhUahBc_iyM&d=uvQyzOR3RFLtOdFPj9O53fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0b5973bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jhUahBc_iyM</a>"},{"pid":"704673e5d133ca6931bd5d264cb445260f524bdf","tid":782108,"uid":159583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"麻友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6aa2f8d2021b39479639d5c1dd5ff5d4c58d98","tid":782108,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"b6eb0a2447cc420d1ea900596f812eddd4c9d54f","tid":782108,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe6aa2f8d2021b39479639d5c1dd5ff5d4c58d98","tid":782108,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"431fbced845bb8dcb51efd7bd752d4cd98b64a95","tid":782108,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704673e5d133ca6931bd5d264cb445260f524bdf","tid":782108,"uid":159583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"麻友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i715.photobucket.com/albums/ww155/kingpenpen/VEGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi715.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fww155%2Fkingpenpen%2FVEGA.jpg&h=b3cab2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5688ade2e856ec0123ff56958728270185f2d606","tid":782108,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"tiger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58126f416ebb907708ec166b1cee02934d30d57","tid":782108,"uid":67081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"8100b966aa7a51ec1400beff9ad249cc83af80b8","tid":782108,"uid